        "subject": "LU-9400 test: conf-sanity 103 remove brackets from routine",
        "message": "LU-9400 test: conf-sanity 103 remove brackets from routine\n\nThe test_renamefs routine in conf-sanity checks if\nthe Lustre file system being tested has a combined MGS and\nMDS by calling the combined_mgs_mds routine. This routine\nis not executed because it is in the \"test\" brackets [].\n\nThe combined_mgs_mds routine should not be called in the\nbrackets.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial combinedmdsmgs=false testlist=conf-sanity\n\nSigned-off-by: James Nunez <james.a.nunez@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I62729c5ce78429c9402ac5e98eb8804436e84bf6\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
